{"sections":{"16510459755928648e":{"type":"text-and-image","custom_css":["@media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {.subheading {margin-bottom: 12px; }}"],"settings":{"custom_id":"","full_width":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/rsz_marco_dal_maso_about_us.jpg","image_mask":"square","image2_mask":"none","subtitle":"Meet Marco","caption":"","title":"DESIGN DIRECTOR AND FOUNDER","text":"<p>Marco Dal Maso learnt the art of jewelry making from his father at an early age. His passions and inspirations amplified throughout the years that he went on to launch his eponymous brand, MARCO DAL MASO, recognised alongside leading international jewelry houses for craftsmanship and design.<\/p>","html":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_labels":"","button_links":"","button_style":"primary","align_text":"left","image_width":"50","layout":"left","body_bg":"#ffffff","divider":false,"top_padding":true,"bottom_padding":true,"lazyload_images":true}},"1651046357f9a17216":{"type":"advanced-content","blocks":{"c4254888-7e90-41d3-a989-5d1d11446bd9":{"type":"liquid","settings":{"code":"<h2> <center>LEARN MARCO’S STORY<\/center><\/h2><br><br>\n\n<video width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\" controls=\"controls\" poster=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/1476\/0022\/files\/marcostoryvideocover.png\">\n  <source src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/1476\/0022\/files\/full.mp4?v=1654782727\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/source>\n  <source src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/1476\/0022\/files\/full.mp4?v=1654782727\" type=\"video\/ogg\"><\/source>\nYour browser does not support the video tag.\n<\/video>","width":"100%","alignment":"center"}}},"block_order":["c4254888-7e90-41d3-a989-5d1d11446bd9"],"custom_css":[".custom-content-fullwidth {padding-top: 75px;}","video {display: inherit;}","@media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {.rte br ~ br {display: none; } video {margin-bottom: 50px; }}"],"settings":{"full_width":true,"space_around":true,"lazyload_images":true}},"1